  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial sample intentionally omits acceptanceCriteria fields on several credibility factors to trigger W-AR-01 (missing acceptance criteria). All 13 ASME V&V 40 factors are addressed; requiredLevel is stated for all assessed factors but the structured acceptanceCriteria link is absent on multiple factors.",
