    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for record. All 13 ASME V&V 40 factors have been addressed. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain as epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. Achieved levels fall below required levels across all assessed factors, confirming the decision outcome of Not Accepted for regulatory submission. The package is accepted as a complete credibility evidence record for internal review purposes.",
